d public relations agency, which managed projects for Tour de Georgia, Larry H. Miller Tour of Utah and USA Cycling.\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4125, \"end\": 4132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peloton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.065206336043683e-15, \"text\": \"Peloton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peloton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peloton\"}, {\"begin\": 4224, \"end\": 4239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9999999998958629, \"rank\": 6.673203305623337e-11, \"text\": \"Tour de Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_Georgia\"}, {\"begin\": 4265, \"end\": 4269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9985628940831078, \"rank\": 0.001374615411695221, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 4274, \"end\": 4285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.616624929816437e-25, \"text\": \"USA Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also founded Bike Alpharetta Inc, a Georgia non-profit to promote safe cycling.\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4309, \"end\": 4319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alpharetta_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9999999907004167, \"rank\": 9.277195566370276e-09, \"text\": \"Alpharetta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alpharetta_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alpharetta_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 4327, \"end\": 4334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc